<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.3.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
  <script>
  $(function() {
    $("#btnLoad").on("click", function() {
      $("#text").load("/rest/1/pages/244");
    });
  });
  </script>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>jQuery Ajax</h1>
  <button id="btnLoad">데이터 로딩</button>
  <p id="text">버튼을 누르면 받아온 데이터가 표시됩니다.</p>
</body>
</html>